<p data-start="327" data-end="541">O Foundry não entende esse pacote externo. Ele espera receber uma URL para um <code data-start="405" data-end="418">module.json</code>; depois lê o campo <code data-start="438" data-end="448">download</code> desse manifesto, baixa o ZIP indicado e o descompacta. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 116px;"><a href="https://foundryvtt.com/article/package-management/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://foundryvtt.com/article/package-management/" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl pe-2 ps-1 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 116px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="./module_files/favicons"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Foundry Virtual Tabletop</span></span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
