<ul data-start="106" data-end="231">
<li data-section-id="p6h7dc" data-start="106" data-end="152">
<p data-start="108" data-end="152"><button aria-label="module.json" class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-token-text-link font-medium" type="button"><span class="relative me-0.75 inline-block h-lh w-4 align-bottom"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" class="absolute top-1/2 h-4 w-4 -translate-y-1/2"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#46a9c5" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span>module.json</button></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kbms4w" data-start="153" data-end="231">
<p data-start="155" data-end="231"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="behavior-btn hover:entity-accent focus-visible:focus-ring entity-underline inline cursor-pointer appearance-none border-0 bg-transparent p-0 text-start align-baseline text-inherit" type="button">dnd5e-character-builder.zip</button></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="233" data-end="477">O ZIP está no formato instalável pelo Foundry, com <code data-start="284" data-end="297">module.json</code>, <code data-start="299" data-end="308">scripts</code>, <code data-start="310" data-end="321">templates</code>, <code data-start="323" data-end="331">styles</code> e demais arquivos diretamente na raiz. O Foundry lê o manifesto e baixa o ZIP indicado no campo <code data-start="428" data-end="438">download</code>. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] translate-y-0.5 animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 116px;"><a href="https://foundryvtt.com/article/package-management/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://foundryvtt.com/article/package-management/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl pe-2 ps-1 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 116px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center gap-1"><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="" width="128" height="128" class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full" src="./module_files/favicons"></span><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Foundry Virtual Tabletop</span></span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+1</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
<h3 data-section-id="a1jk8d" data-start="479" data-end="506">Configuração da release</h3>
<p data-start="508" data-end="523">Use exatamente:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="525" data-end="592"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-(--code-block-surface) corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl [--code-block-surface:var(--bg-elevated-secondary)] dark:[--code-block-surface:var(--composer-surface-primary)] lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-18ad762e.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼs ͼ16"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>Tag: v0.9.1
Release title: Character Builder 0.9.1 Beta</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="594" data-end="624">Não renomeie os dois arquivos.</p>
<p data-start="626" data-end="710">Depois de publicar a release, a URL para instalação e para cadastro no Foundry será:</p>
